      <odd id="aspace_c9c766508d3f90520608ffb9f353ade6">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 48-A (YRG 48-A), Yale pictorial records and collections.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_e35a3e29141eb833a4ca06140aba0e2b">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The materials were a gift of Paul H. Silverstone, 2004, 2008.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
